{"tid":2252043,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中學生承認管有雷射筆 蘇文隆下令還押候判","createTime":"2020-10-21T08:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T13:14:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8e0ffa205b17693f527d561a8287f704726a2c","tid":2252043,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10555&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=0e6eb57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10555</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官<br />\n#1014大埔 #答辯<br />\n<br />\n陳（17）<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器。<br />\n（即雷射光束裝置，一支雷射筆。）<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n2019年10月14日，當天大埔區有示威活動，警員於大元邨一帶巡邏，期間被告連同3-4個黑衣人大叫「死黑警」，警員於是上前截查，在大埔安慈路大埔中心巴士總站外成功截查被告，其餘的黑衣人則逃離現場。警員於被告的背囊內搜出多樣物品，例如雷射筆、黑色頭盔、兩罐壓縮氣體、手袖、眼罩和手套等。被控無合法權限管有雷射光束裝置，即雷射筆一枝，化驗所報告指該雷射筆在80米內照射可以對人的眼睛造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n被告‼️認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\n求情：<br />\n被告樂於助人，參加多項義務工作，現就讀中學，與父母、姐姐居於一起。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至11月4日1430於粉嶺裁判法院第一庭判刑，待索取勞教中心及更生中心報告，‼️期間還押‼️。"},{"pid":"7d2a2b4416fc60e3bcb2b73e90aef4b9023f1634","tid":2252043,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"又係佢"},{"pid":"a9504e1679e9e536dc8f2cff803852a500d2874c","tid":2252043,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32b2649a069ec1f6bb175846dd7bd791662a46d4","tid":2252043,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd0e5df2c9b85b806671397eeaa7f11f838883b","tid":2252043,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot